{"title":"金缕曲——痛悼程子华同志逝世","authors":["熊复"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金缕曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——痛悼程子华同志逝世"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微雨悲歌彻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问解州、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄安在？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河呜咽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少小横刀驰驱日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志壮山高水阔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更立马、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江南塞北。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还把精魂输重造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总通宵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呕尽心头血。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"君去矣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音徽烈！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同窗共读从何说？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫回首、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载言载笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"议论风发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗尽胸中幽忧处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱看人间春色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算赢得、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寸丹如雪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后死当知兴华事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最艰难、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨砺操清节。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长梦断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京华月。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９９１年４月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后记：程子华同志逝世，不胜伤痛。十日参加遗体告别仪式归来，作《金缕曲》以悼念之。词中称“同窗共读”，盖指我和他于１９７５年３月至６月间，同在中央读书班学习。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}